HEADWORD: Illegal
<hw>Il*le"gal</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>il-</ets> not + <ets>legal</ets>: cf. F.
<ets>ill⟦eacute⟧gal</ets>.]</ety> <def>Not according to, or authorized
by, law; specif., contrary to, or in violation of, human law; unlawful;
illicit; hence, immoral; <as>as, an <ex>illegal</ex> act;
<ex>illegal</ex> trade; <ex>illegal</ex> love.</as></def> <rj><au>Bp.
Burnet.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

